1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 17]

5
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,940
Guard yourselves well

6
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:14,420
once you go inside.

7
00:01:14,670 --> 00:01:16,450
Do not let the demonic energy

8
00:01:16,830 --> 00:01:17,700
corrupt your minds.

9
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:34,890
This is a Linglong Talisman.

10
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:35,890
In times of danger,

11
00:01:35,910 --> 00:01:37,980
you can use it to call nearby fellow disciples.

12
00:01:38,750 --> 00:01:39,340
Remember,

13
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,250
never go off alone.

14
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:14,900
Set out now.

15
00:02:15,670 --> 00:02:16,620
- Yes. - Yes.

16
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,690
Lifei, join my team.

17
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,130
I'll go with Zhaomin.

18
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,300
Let's go.

19
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:38,900
Zhaomin.

20
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:41,300
Alright. This mission is urgent.

21
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,500
Let's head in...

22
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:50,090
Looks like it's just the three of us

23
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,940
on this team.

24
00:02:57,830 --> 00:02:58,530
Lei?

25
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:00,530
Fine.

26
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:02,900
Now we have four.

27
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:07,850
Let's go.

28
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:20,780
Everyone, don't be afraid.

29
00:03:21,110 --> 00:03:21,900
I'm here.

30
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,410
Before I came, I performed a divination.

31
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:26,620
It said we'd turn danger into safety.

32
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,460
What's this?

33
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,570
Scratches.

34
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,620
It was bound by spirit-locking ropes.

35
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,650
It must have struggled desperately before death,

36
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,530
leaving marks that won't fade

37
00:03:48,830 --> 00:03:49,620
for centuries.

38
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:55,060
It seems to be the Altar of Martyrs of Xingzheng Hall.

39
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,940
Even if they were demon scum,

40
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:59,620
this is a cruel death.

41
00:04:06,270 --> 00:04:07,220
Why keep them

42
00:04:08,110 --> 00:04:09,780
locked up here even after death,

43
00:04:09,990 --> 00:04:10,810
humiliating them like this?

44
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,810
For centuries,

45
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:16,620
the immortal sects have known little about demons.

46
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:18,770
So the elders from the previous generation

47
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:20,980
captured many demons during the war

48
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:23,500
and imprisoned them here for interrogation,

49
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,500
hoping to find their weaknesses.

50
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,210
Did they find out anything?

51
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,370
They say demons fear not even death.

52
00:04:30,790 --> 00:04:32,330
The elders got nothing.

53
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,620
Zhaomin, watch out!

54
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,740
Get down.

55
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:13,690
See? Danger turned to safety.

56
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:17,890
By the way,

57
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:19,770
have you heard about the Sea Calamity war

58
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,890
five hundred years ago?

59
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,180
I often hear the elders talk about it.

60
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:25,130
I've also read some books about it.

61
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,980
They all say our sects suffered heavy losses.

62
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,100
Didn't expect the demons to suffer just as badly.

63
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:32,300
Heaven and earth are indifferent,

64
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,890
treating all things like straw dogs.

65
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:35,980
The next Sea Calamity

66
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,810
is less than two years away.

67
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:45,370
It's a Linglong Talisman.

68
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,330
A fellow disciple is in danger!

69
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,060
Where are you guys?

70
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,250
Get away!

71
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,420
Lifei.

72
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:52,860
Lifei!

73
00:06:58,150 --> 00:06:58,890
Help!

74
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,860
Yue?

75
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,690
Zhuyan?

76
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,210
How did this happen?

77
00:08:21,150 --> 00:08:21,770
Oh no.

78
00:08:22,030 --> 00:08:23,100
The disciples are still inside!

79
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,180
Guangwei!

80
00:08:24,910 --> 00:08:25,450
Let's go.

81
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:48,690
You're awake.

82
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:53,260
Qin?

83
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,610
Lifei,

84
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,020
you were corrupted by demonic energy.

85
00:08:57,350 --> 00:08:58,610
I'm healing you.

86
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:14,730
No.

87
00:09:23,350 --> 00:09:24,380
No, thanks.

88
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,260
I have a Linglong Talisman.

89
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,420
A distant call won't help as fast as I can.

90
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,730
Let me help you.

91
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,090
Lifei, don't be afraid.

92
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,610
I really mean well for you.

93
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:45,210
You...

94
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:56,060
If you agree to be with me,

95
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:59,180
I'll treat you well.

96
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:02,970
When I become the head of Wuyue Court someday,

97
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:06,210
you'll stand above all others.

98
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:13,900
Get away!

99
00:10:24,110 --> 00:10:24,660
Let go!

100
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:25,970
Let go!

101
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:26,780
Me?

102
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,570
Let go now!

103
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,690
I...

104
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:31,450
I want to...

105
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,260
Let go!

106
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,970
- I... - Let go!

107
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:36,450
I want to, but...

108
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,090
The Achillea Bead?

109
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,210
That's incredible.

110
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:22,810
Go!

111
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:29,140
Go now.

112
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,970
You were corrupted by demonic energy?

113
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:42,090
Wake up.

114
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:43,420
Wake up!

115
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,660
Xiuyuan.

116
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:05,970
Have you really fallen into demonhood?

117
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:38,260
Lifei.

118
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:40,300
Let's go.

119
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,210
It's Zhuyan! Found the source of demonic energy!

120
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:08,780
Lei!

121
00:13:11,350 --> 00:13:11,810
Cailing.

122
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,610
Yue.

123
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,090
Too bad Zhuyan got away in the end.

124
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:35,380
It's okay.

125
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:35,970
Careful.

126
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,540
- Careful. - Go sit down.

127
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:42,540
Easy.

128
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:45,060
Are you okay?

129
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:45,940
I'm fine.

130
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:47,210
Everyone, move!

131
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:48,090
Get out of the way!

132
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:49,780
Jiang Lifei

133
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,180
is a demon spy!

134
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:54,420
Demon spy?

135
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:55,540
A spy?

136
00:13:55,540 --> 00:13:56,180
She's a demon spy?

137
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:56,810
I knew it.

138
00:13:58,350 --> 00:13:58,850
No wonder...

139
00:13:58,870 --> 00:13:59,810
I could tell something was off about her.

140
00:13:59,830 --> 00:14:00,260
Right!

141
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:02,420
Master,

142
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,090
I saw

143
00:14:04,110 --> 00:14:06,140
Jiang Lifei resonate with the skeleton of that Lion-Eagle.

144
00:14:06,590 --> 00:14:08,330
I thought she had been corrupted by demonic energy

145
00:14:08,590 --> 00:14:09,450
and wanted to help her.

146
00:14:09,870 --> 00:14:11,180
But she attacked me.

147
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:12,210
The technique was strange.

148
00:14:12,630 --> 00:14:13,900
Nothing like what we practice here.

149
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:17,850
You're projecting!

150
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:19,900
If you thought something was wrong with me,

151
00:14:20,110 --> 00:14:21,570
why didn't you use the Linglong Talisman to summon our sect members

152
00:14:21,590 --> 00:14:22,610
instead of knocking me out?

153
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:26,730
Oh my!

154
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:28,690
You all heard that, right?

155
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:30,690
My disciple was knocked out by him!

156
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,060
Lifei,

157
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:35,490
are you still feeling unwell?

158
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,300
Yes, Master.

159
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:38,450
You have no idea.

160
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:40,850
My head is still spinning.

161
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,690
See?

162
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:43,540
Why

163
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,140
did you knock out Lifei?

164
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,020
What were you trying to do?

165
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:46,900
Elder Chongyi,

166
00:14:47,710 --> 00:14:48,540
you can't trust

167
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:49,300
the words of a spy.

168
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:52,210
Qin's ability and character

169
00:14:52,990 --> 00:14:54,900
are well known to everyone.

170
00:14:55,590 --> 00:14:57,780
If he truly had feelings for Jiang,

171
00:14:58,830 --> 00:15:01,210
he wouldn't need to resort to such tricks.

172
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:06,970
Perhaps someone was seducing him.

173
00:15:07,590 --> 00:15:09,020
Guangwei, Baifu,

174
00:15:09,470 --> 00:15:10,900
are you bullying us just because

175
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:12,570
we have fewer people on Zhuiyu Peak?

176
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:17,450
Qin,

177
00:15:18,230 --> 00:15:19,850
how are you so sure that Lifei

178
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:21,540
is a demon spy?

179
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:23,330
She can absorb spirit energy.

180
00:15:23,590 --> 00:15:25,330
Just like that traitor's evil spirit-draining technique.

181
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:37,180
Elder Cuixuan,

182
00:15:38,590 --> 00:15:40,060
if Lifei were truly a demon spy,

183
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:41,300
would she have risked her life

184
00:15:41,510 --> 00:15:42,380
fighting Zhuyan?

185
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:44,780
Yue was there too.

186
00:15:45,510 --> 00:15:46,570
Please tell everyone

187
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:48,810
what happened, Yue.

188
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:09,490
I was knocked unconscious by Zhuyan.

189
00:16:10,460 --> 00:16:13,090
When I woke up, Zhuyan had already fled.

190
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,570
I don't know

191
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:18,330
what happened in between.

192
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:19,900
You...

193
00:16:39,820 --> 00:16:41,090
Here's the thing.

194
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:42,940
Lifei's techniques

195
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:44,810
were all taught by me.

196
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:47,300
Some of them are indeed a bit unconventional.

197
00:16:48,110 --> 00:16:49,850
As for absorbing spirit power,

198
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:51,780
Qin,

199
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,780
you must be mistaken.

200
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:56,090
Ever since Lifei absorbed

201
00:16:56,110 --> 00:16:57,780
the Achillea Bead's spirit power,

202
00:16:58,100 --> 00:17:00,780
she's had trouble controlling the energy inside her.

203
00:17:01,350 --> 00:17:03,260
So Qin was likely injured

204
00:17:03,350 --> 00:17:07,050
by the Achillea Bead's power.

205
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:08,730
It's a misunderstanding.

206
00:17:10,460 --> 00:17:12,530
Since both sides stick to their own stories,

207
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:14,730
let's take this to the punishment hall.

208
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:16,620
Truth

209
00:17:17,070 --> 00:17:18,340
will reveal itself then.

210
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:20,250
Cuixuan.

211
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:23,970
I have a way

212
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:25,180
to find out the truth.

213
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:33,380
Are you willing to try?

214
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:35,180
I am.

215
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:38,490
So...

216
00:17:38,940 --> 00:17:39,660
So am I.

217
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:51,100
I recently came across a Lingzhi.

218
00:17:52,700 --> 00:17:54,050
It has a peculiar effect.

219
00:17:54,980 --> 00:17:57,580
It makes people speak the truth.

220
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:07,100
Lifei, you go first.

221
00:18:21,710 --> 00:18:22,340
Lifei,

222
00:18:22,980 --> 00:18:24,900
how did you meet Qin Yangling?

223
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:31,860
Qin said he wanted to heal me.

224
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:33,770
I wanted to use the Linglong Talisman,

225
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,940
but he tried to knock me out.

226
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:37,580
And he said

227
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:39,290
if I agreed to be with him,

228
00:18:39,710 --> 00:18:41,580
when he became the head of Wuyue Court someday,

229
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:43,340
I'd stand above all others.

230
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:46,340
I tried to fight back, and he ran off.

231
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:15,490
Elder Dongyang,

232
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,420
Master,

233
00:19:16,980 --> 00:19:17,770
I was wrong.

234
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:21,180
But I really was trying to heal Lifei.

235
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:23,690
Somehow, I was overcome by dark thoughts.

236
00:19:23,990 --> 00:19:25,340
I don't know what came over me.

237
00:19:25,470 --> 00:19:26,530
And I don't know why

238
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:28,010
I have come to covet Lifei.

239
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:31,180
What did you do to Lifei?

240
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:32,210
Speak!

241
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:34,690
Speak!

242
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:37,010
You admit you assaulted Lifei?

243
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:39,450
I...

244
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:41,420
I don't remember.

245
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:42,580
You wretch!

246
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:44,490
I'll strip your cultivation right now!

247
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,580
Cuixuan, calm down!

248
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:50,180
Qin has always been upright.

249
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:53,100
It must be the overwhelming demonic energy within the valley

250
00:19:53,470 --> 00:19:55,340
that made him lose his mind.

251
00:19:56,270 --> 00:19:59,900
This could be the work of the demon spy as well.

252
00:20:00,550 --> 00:20:01,730
Demons are cunning and deceitful.

253
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,140
Before we get to the bottom of this,

254
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:05,100
we must not fall for their tricks

255
00:20:05,220 --> 00:20:06,140
and weaken our own ranks.

256
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:08,730
Fine.

257
00:20:09,470 --> 00:20:10,820
Very well.

258
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:12,010
Let's

259
00:20:12,470 --> 00:20:14,340
just pretend Lifei

260
00:20:14,660 --> 00:20:16,620
was never wronged

261
00:20:17,030 --> 00:20:19,180
or mistreated.

262
00:20:19,310 --> 00:20:20,900
Let's just drop it!

263
00:20:34,620 --> 00:20:35,940
Your resolve was weak,

264
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:38,210
so the demons took advantage!

265
00:20:39,660 --> 00:20:40,900
Go to Yunhai Peak now

266
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:42,050
for punishment and reflection!

267
00:20:54,710 --> 00:20:56,180
The demon beast Zhuyan has escaped.

268
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:57,770
Notify all nine states' sects

269
00:20:58,070 --> 00:21:00,100
to spare no effort in tracking it down!

270
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:44,490
Who's there?

271
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,250
Lei Xiuyuan?

272
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:01,180
What are you doing?

273
00:22:06,120 --> 00:22:06,860
I said

274
00:22:08,180 --> 00:22:09,380
anyone who dares to hurt Lifei

275
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,660
will die by my hand.

276
00:22:26,990 --> 00:22:29,250
Lei, I didn't mean it.

277
00:22:50,230 --> 00:22:51,100
If you kill me,

278
00:22:51,700 --> 00:22:53,690
the elders won't let you go.

279
00:22:54,360 --> 00:22:56,860
And it'll drag Lifei into it.

280
00:22:57,230 --> 00:22:57,730
Shut up!

281
00:22:59,860 --> 00:23:00,770
You don't deserve to say her name.

282
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:08,860
How do you have demonic energy on you?

283
00:23:13,700 --> 00:23:14,180
No.

284
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:17,770
You were tainted by demonic energy

285
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:19,900
and went berserk,

286
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:23,250
and I was forced to kill you

287
00:23:23,660 --> 00:23:24,970
to root out the demon spy.

288
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:27,620
Die!

289
00:23:59,470 --> 00:24:00,970
You dare bully my disciple?

290
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:02,450
You're asking for it!

291
00:24:02,660 --> 00:24:03,290
He deserves to die.

292
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:05,450
Sir, why are you stopping me?

293
00:24:09,270 --> 00:24:11,860
Cuixuan is already suspicious

294
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:13,340
of you and Lifei.

295
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:16,820
Just don't stir up more trouble, alright?

296
00:24:22,710 --> 00:24:23,970
Did you pick up

297
00:24:24,620 --> 00:24:26,180
some demonic energy in Lilie Valley too?

298
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:33,140
Go back and expel it with your cultivation.

299
00:24:37,180 --> 00:24:38,690
That snake Qin Yangling.

300
00:24:38,990 --> 00:24:40,530
He hid his true colors so well all along.

301
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:43,010
Elder Cuixuan is obviously protecting his own.

302
00:24:43,990 --> 00:24:45,100
And worst of all,

303
00:24:45,620 --> 00:24:48,010
they even accused Lifei of seducing him.

304
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,340
Come on, look at Lifei,

305
00:24:50,510 --> 00:24:51,730
who could she even seduce?

306
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:55,250
Lifei, take it easy.

307
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:55,860
Drink slowly.

308
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:56,860
There's more in the kitchen.

309
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,820
Appearances are deceptive.

310
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:02,860
Lei Xiuyuan is a good one, though.

311
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:05,860
He stood up to protect you just now.

312
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:11,620
If Lifei were truly a demon spy,

313
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:12,730
would she have risked her life?

314
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:13,660
Lifei,

315
00:25:13,990 --> 00:25:16,050
how did you and Lei run into Zhuyan?

316
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,420
And how did it escape later?

317
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:19,820
We just ran into it.

318
00:25:20,340 --> 00:25:21,620
Then, when everyone showed up,

319
00:25:21,710 --> 00:25:22,530
it ran off.

320
00:25:25,600 --> 00:25:27,290
Have you ever considered this?

321
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,690
Without a spy helping from the inside,

322
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:32,340
how did that scumbag Zhuyan escape?

323
00:25:36,030 --> 00:25:38,420
You all know Zhuyan, right?

324
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:42,290
It's one of the four great demon beasts.

325
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:44,380
With it on the loose,

326
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:47,860
who knows how many sect disciples will suffer?

327
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:52,010
Peaceful days are over.

328
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:04,050
Xiuyuan.

329
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:24,420
Lifei?

330
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,580
I came to ask you something.

331
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:29,580
Don't overthink it.

332
00:26:33,070 --> 00:26:33,660
Go ahead.

333
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:40,340
Are you hiding something from me?

334
00:26:44,710 --> 00:26:46,100
That time in the academy's forbidden area.

335
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:47,620
And this time too.

336
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:51,820
Every time you're corrupted by demonic energy,

337
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:53,820
you react strangely.

338
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,450
And

339
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:58,900
your eyes

340
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:02,100
turn golden.

341
00:27:04,230 --> 00:27:05,530
And at the Altar of Martyrs.

342
00:27:06,310 --> 00:27:07,250
Were those skulls

343
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,100
and black demon spirits

344
00:27:09,840 --> 00:27:11,100
summoned by you?

345
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,210
Fine, don't tell me.

346
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:26,660
Anyway, after Lilie Valley,

347
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:28,860
we're even.

348
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,730
Let's just stay out of each other's way

349
00:27:30,990 --> 00:27:32,010
and keep our distance.

350
00:27:40,790 --> 00:27:41,860
I've been a spirit magnet since childhood.

351
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:43,340
I'm not like others.

352
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:44,580
My master said

353
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,940
that no two people are exactly alike.

354
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,420
No need to force everyone to be the same.

355
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:51,820
Watch out for yourself.

356
00:27:57,790 --> 00:27:58,180
Lifei.

357
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,420
Leave with me.

358
00:28:02,600 --> 00:28:03,250
What did you say?

359
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:04,420
Let's leave together.

360
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:05,210
Go back to Qingqiu.

361
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,140
The Sea Calamity and the demons

362
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:08,730
have nothing to do with us.

363
00:28:10,030 --> 00:28:11,250
You're talking nonsense. Let go.

364
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,490
Lifei, you said

365
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,210
you didn't want to be bullied.

366
00:28:14,990 --> 00:28:16,380
You want to sleep soundly and live freely.

367
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,940
But we're not living freely here.

368
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,690
Your senior brother isn't here.

369
00:28:20,710 --> 00:28:21,580
Your master isn't here.

370
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,340
Why stay?

371
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:26,660
Let's leave together.

372
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:32,010
I won't hurt you again.

373
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:34,620
We'll leave now.

374
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:39,620
Let go...

375
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,660
How dare you, you wretch!

376
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:50,010
Are you trying to follow in Hu Jiaping's footsteps?

377
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:58,450
Well,

378
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,660
sir,

379
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:01,660
Elder Dongyang's medicine for Lei

380
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,250
has been delivered.

381
00:29:02,270 --> 00:29:03,210
I'll be leaving now.

382
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:15,380
You're blinded by lust

383
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,450
and refuse to learn.

384
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:19,050
I'd rather strip your cultivation myself

385
00:29:19,710 --> 00:29:21,730
than let you betray the sect

386
00:29:21,750 --> 00:29:23,210
like Hu Jiaping.

387
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:28,420
Reflect on yourself here.

388
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,180
Can't you control her?

389
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,140
First, she messed with Qin

390
00:30:06,750 --> 00:30:08,140
and got him banished to Yunhai Peak.

391
00:30:08,600 --> 00:30:11,490
Now she is targeting my disciple at Yaogang Peak

392
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:13,730
and nearly talked him into eloping!

393
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:17,180
Guangwei,

394
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:19,580
how can you say that?

395
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:22,180
She was just visiting him out of concern.

396
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:24,140
Spare me!

397
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:25,290
I'm telling you,

398
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,380
tell Jiang Lifei

399
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:29,100
to stay away from Yaoguang Peak!

400
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:29,940
I can't control that.

401
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:32,050
Young people's affairs are beyond me.

402
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:34,010
I can't just lock my disciple up

403
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:36,100
in Danxue every time like you do.

404
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,450
Your disciple can be content with mediocrity.

405
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:40,290
But Lei Xiuyuan carries great responsibility.

406
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:42,730
I don't want to see him expelled!

407
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:44,100
Then expel him.

408
00:30:44,230 --> 00:30:45,210
I'll take him.

409
00:30:45,710 --> 00:30:47,380
He's here often enough anyway.

410
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:50,340
Chongyi,

411
00:30:51,270 --> 00:30:52,620
the Sea Calamity is coming.

412
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:54,730
How long can you shield them?

413
00:30:55,990 --> 00:30:58,580
Have you forgotten what happened 500 years ago?

414
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:01,490
When we're gone,

415
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:03,050
who will protect them?

416
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:05,340
Only through dedicated cultivation

417
00:31:06,120 --> 00:31:08,340
can we truly help them.

418
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:12,100
Jiang Lifei has a unique constitution.

419
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:14,010
She's your disciple.

420
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:16,050
It's fine if you want to protect her.

421
00:31:17,550 --> 00:31:19,050
But can you really not see

422
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:21,580
that she's different from others?

423
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:24,420
When the Sea Calamity comes,

424
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:26,580
creatures across the sea will invade the Central Plains.

425
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:27,380
Suspicion

426
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,860
will spread among the people.

427
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:31,140
Who will be able to protect her then?

428
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:39,100
Across the sea?

429
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:52,010
Golden eyes?

430
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,690
Spirit-attracting?

431
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:56,580
Are there such constitutions across the sea?

432
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:01,420
Gelin.

433
00:32:04,230 --> 00:32:05,210
Why aren't you training?

434
00:32:06,070 --> 00:32:07,050
Why train?

435
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:10,380
Might as well end it all.

436
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:11,820
Why waste the time?

437
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,620
Since you haven't made up your mind,

438
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:15,180
live each day

439
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:16,490
to the fullest.

440
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:18,970
Whether life is long or short,

441
00:32:19,750 --> 00:32:20,580
it should be lived without regret.

442
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,340
What are you talking about,

443
00:32:22,360 --> 00:32:22,970
Lu?

444
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,530
I'm still young,

445
00:32:24,550 --> 00:32:25,250
and you're cursing me to die?

446
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:27,250
You're not going to try... again?

447
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:29,140
I mean, I can already summon spirits.

448
00:32:29,960 --> 00:32:31,050
More training is just a waste of time.

449
00:32:33,030 --> 00:32:34,620
Spirit summoning is the hardest technique of the Sea Sect.

450
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:35,970
You really mastered it?

451
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,820
You don't believe me?

452
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:41,140
How about this?

453
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,420
Let's make a bet.

454
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,210
If I've really mastered it,

455
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:45,970
you give me something.

456
00:32:48,230 --> 00:32:48,660
Deal.

457
00:33:15,990 --> 00:33:16,620
Lu,

458
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:18,050
that pendant of yours is nice.

459
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:19,010
Give it to me.

460
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,180
Are you sure you want it?

461
00:33:35,550 --> 00:33:36,050
I...

462
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:37,690
I was joking.

463
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:42,340
Oh, Lu,

464
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:43,970
do you know if anyone

465
00:33:43,990 --> 00:33:45,420
across the sea has golden eyes?

466
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:46,860
Or a spirit-attracting constitution?

467
00:33:48,750 --> 00:33:49,820
I don't know about spirit-attracting.

468
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,490
But golden eyes...

469
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:54,970
They say the Demon Lord Yecha

470
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,180
had golden eyes.

471
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,210
Demon Lord Yecha?

472
00:34:04,230 --> 00:34:04,620
Wait,

473
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,380
the Demon Lord is hideous.

474
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:08,130
How could Lei Xiuyuan be him?

475
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:10,820
Gelin probably got it wrong.

476
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:12,380
Forget it.

477
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:13,380
I'll look it up myself.

478
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:16,340
Oh, right,

479
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:19,050
Master has a book about the lands across the sea.

480
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,490
What's that sound?

481
00:34:33,700 --> 00:34:35,530
Cuixuan, the Pangu Bell is ringing.

482
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:36,940
Has something big happened?

483
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:40,450
The disciples tracking Zhuyan report

484
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:43,130
that it has broken into the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff.

485
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:46,820
I knew

486
00:34:47,110 --> 00:34:48,220
that Outcast Tomb across the sea

487
00:34:48,470 --> 00:34:49,740
would eventually bring disaster.

488
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:51,010
If only back then...

489
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:52,940
Don't bring up the past.

490
00:34:53,780 --> 00:34:55,820
The Outcast Tomb has been sealed for centuries,

491
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:57,820
and no one has set foot there.

492
00:34:58,510 --> 00:35:00,090
Even those who stumbled in

493
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,780
never came back.

494
00:35:02,240 --> 00:35:03,820
No one knows

495
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,860
what's inside to this day.

496
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:08,650
After all that effort to dodge the immortal sects' pursuit,

497
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,570
Zhuyan fought its way into the Outcast Tomb.

498
00:35:10,990 --> 00:35:11,820
Why?

499
00:35:17,030 --> 00:35:19,530
The Outcast Tomb is full of traps.

500
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:21,780
Perhaps the most dangerous place

501
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:24,380
is the safest in the entire Central Plains.

502
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:25,340
That

503
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:27,450
could be the demons' stronghold.

504
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,740
This is a serious matter.

505
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:40,220
Whether it's a stronghold

506
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:42,450
or a trap,

507
00:35:43,820 --> 00:35:46,260
I'm going there myself

508
00:35:46,820 --> 00:35:49,010
to get to the bottom of it.

509
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:52,700
Lifei.

510
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:54,340
Lifei?

511
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:11,650
Lifei?

512
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:23,420
Enjoy reading it?

513
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:26,260
Can't read a character of it. What is all this?

514
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:30,860
Master.

515
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:33,300
Silly girl.

516
00:36:33,420 --> 00:36:34,130
What book is that?

517
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:35,130
You were so absorbed

518
00:36:35,150 --> 00:36:36,300
that you didn't even notice me come in.

519
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:39,380
I picked it up by the roadside somewhere.

520
00:36:40,340 --> 00:36:41,780
The demons across the sea are about to invade.

521
00:36:41,820 --> 00:36:42,530
So I'm doing some research.

522
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:47,420
You can read this?

523
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:48,940
I can read anything.

524
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:53,860
You know, this book

525
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:56,340
is quite detailed.

526
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:58,820
It even covers secret histories

527
00:36:58,860 --> 00:37:00,940
like the Outcast Tomb across the sea.

528
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:02,530
Outcast Tomb?

529
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:03,860
What place is that?

530
00:37:09,190 --> 00:37:10,780
That's actually why

531
00:37:10,820 --> 00:37:12,010
I came to see you today.

532
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:14,490
Remember that Zhuyan who escaped

533
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:15,380
a while back?

534
00:37:16,720 --> 00:37:18,010
That scumbag

535
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:20,610
has holed up in the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff.

536
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:22,860
Cuixuan wants to

537
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:25,820
take a group of elite disciples there.

538
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:28,650
Do you think you'd be left out?

539
00:37:29,190 --> 00:37:29,860
So

540
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:33,650
I think you need to fall sick starting today

541
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,570
and stay sick until they get back.

542
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:37,260
Get it?

543
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:41,260
Master is tied to the world across the sea.

544
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:44,090
I should take this chance to find out more.

545
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:46,260
We are facing a massive threat.

546
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:48,610
How can I pretend to be sick and hide?

547
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:50,970
What's with the outburst? Have you lost your mind?

548
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:52,780
Last time it was for the Achillea Bead.

549
00:37:52,980 --> 00:37:53,740
What is it this time?

550
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:56,220
Master,

551
00:37:56,820 --> 00:37:58,220
you just said

552
00:37:58,670 --> 00:37:59,650
all the disciples are going.

553
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:01,340
So Lei Xiuyuan will be going too.

554
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:03,300
How can I miss that?

555
00:38:06,990 --> 00:38:09,530
I feel like I'm losing control over you.

556
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:12,740
Fine.

557
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:15,010
I'll give you a protective sword.

558
00:38:24,980 --> 00:38:25,860
White Cliff is dangerous.

559
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:27,610
Be careful in everything.

560
00:38:28,150 --> 00:38:29,970
If you run into something you can't handle,

561
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:31,490
don't push yourself.

562
00:38:31,510 --> 00:38:32,260
Run straight back

563
00:38:32,550 --> 00:38:34,010
to Zhuiyu Peak.

564
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:34,570
Remember,

565
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:36,090
once you're back here,

566
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:38,450
no one can hurt you.

567
00:39:15,860 --> 00:39:16,940
Still won't admit you're wrong?

568
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:20,860
Do you really want me to destroy your spirit root

569
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:22,260
and strip your cultivation?

570
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:23,530
I'm not wrong.

571
00:39:24,860 --> 00:39:25,450
Why should I admit it?

572
00:39:48,590 --> 00:39:50,220
Zhuyan has fled to White Cliff.

573
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,090
Go with Cuixuan

574
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:53,970
and make up for your mistake.

575
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:07,490
Come in,

576
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:08,940
Lei.

577
00:40:35,550 --> 00:40:36,780
Why did Zhuyan head to White Cliff?

578
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:40,130
How would I know?

579
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:41,900
You let it out.

580
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:43,420
How can you not know?

581
00:40:46,980 --> 00:40:48,860
Zhuyan's chains were deliberately cut.

582
00:40:50,110 --> 00:40:50,860
You called for help,

583
00:40:51,470 --> 00:40:52,340
but your breathing was steady

584
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:53,900
and didn't falter for a second.

585
00:40:55,630 --> 00:40:56,650
And that last whistle

586
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:57,970
was you too.

587
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:02,260
Yue,

588
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,530
what are you after?

589
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,220
What am I after?

590
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,780
You, of course.

591
00:41:18,110 --> 00:41:19,010
Who are you really?

592
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,940
When you reach White Cliff,

593
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:23,650
you'll know everything.

594
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:29,260
Aren't you afraid I'll tell Master all of this?

595
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:38,650
I know

596
00:41:40,150 --> 00:41:40,970
you won't.

597
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,340
He's here too.

598
00:42:24,220 --> 00:42:25,220
What a pain.

599
00:42:25,700 --> 00:42:27,090
He's done reflecting already?

600
00:42:27,470 --> 00:42:29,090
He's trying to make up for his mistake

601
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:30,300
and make this all go away.

602
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:32,780
No wonder my divination last night warned me

603
00:42:33,320 --> 00:42:34,570
about a backstabber on this trip.

604
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:38,920
[The Eternal Fragrance]

605
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:40,720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

606
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:55,480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

607
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:58,480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

608
00:42:58,560 --> 00:43:01,800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

609
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:05,080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

610
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:09,080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

611
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:12,560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

612
00:43:12,720 --> 00:43:18,800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

613
00:43:19,080 --> 00:43:23,200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

614
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:26,160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

615
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:28,280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

616
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:32,720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

617
00:43:32,880 --> 00:43:36,720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

618
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:40,080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

619
00:43:40,160 --> 00:43:46,280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

620
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:50,200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

621
00:44:03,440 --> 00:44:07,200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

622
00:44:07,400 --> 00:44:10,200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

623
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:13,680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

624
00:44:13,680 --> 00:44:17,000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

625
00:44:17,160 --> 00:44:21,000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

626
00:44:21,160 --> 00:44:24,360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

627
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:30,440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

628
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:34,920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

629
00:44:35,200 --> 00:44:37,960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

630
00:44:38,160 --> 00:44:40,000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

631
00:44:40,160 --> 00:44:44,360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

632
00:44:44,600 --> 00:44:48,480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

633
00:44:48,720 --> 00:44:51,760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

634
00:44:51,960 --> 00:44:58,680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

635
00:44:58,720 --> 00:45:02,680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

636
00:45:02,920 --> 00:45:05,680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

637
00:45:05,800 --> 00:45:07,720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

638
00:45:07,880 --> 00:45:12,160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

639
00:45:12,360 --> 00:45:16,200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

640
00:45:16,440 --> 00:45:19,560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

641
00:45:19,600 --> 00:45:25,600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

642
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:30,360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
